# ============================================================
# Chip-Launcher-ForMatter — Git Commit Template
# ============================================================
# Lines starting with '#' are comments and will be stripped.
# Write your commit message below.
# ============================================================

# <type>(<scope>): <subject>
# |<----  72 chars max  ---->|
# 
# <body>
# |<---  wrap at 72 chars  --->|
#
# <footer>
# ============================================================
# Type (required):
#   feat      — New feature
#   fix       — Bug fix
#   docs      — Documentation only
#   style     — Formatting, whitespace (no code change)
#   refactor  — Code refactor (no feature, no fix)
#   perf      — Performance improvement
#   test      — Tests
#   chore     — Build, config, deps, tooling
#   ci        — CI/CD
#   revert    — Revert a previous commit
# ============================================================
# Scope (optional, recommended):
#   script    — matter_start.sh
#   docs      — README / documentation
#   config    — Configuration / env
#   thread    — Thread network logic
#   wifi      — WiFi commissioning logic
#   persist   — Data persistence
#   ci        — CI / workflows
# ============================================================
# Subject rules:
#   - Use imperative, present tense: "add" not "added"
#   - No period at the end
#   - Capitalize first letter
#   - Max 72 characters
# ============================================================
# Body (optional):
#   - Explain WHAT and WHY, not HOW
#   - Wrap at 72 characters
#   - Separate from subject by a blank line
# ============================================================
# 提交类型(必填):
#   feat      — 新功能
#   fix       — 缺陷修复
#   docs      — 文档更新
#   style     — 代码格式(不影响逻辑)
#   refactor  — 重构(无功能变更)
#   perf      — 性能优化
#   test      — 测试
#   chore     — 构建/配置/依赖/工具
#   ci        — CI/CD
#   revert    — 回滚
# ============================================================
# 主题规则:
#   - 使用祈使语气、现在时态
#   - 末尾不加句号
#   - 首字母大写
#   - 最长 72 字符
# ============================================================
# Examples:
#   feat(script): add auto-generated Node ID with dedup check
#   fix(thread): handle OTBR restart dataset recovery
#   docs(readme): add bilingual README with architecture diagrams
#   feat(persist): implement per-node fabric storage isolation
#   fix(wifi): validate SSID password before chip-tool invocation
# ============================================================

# Write your commit message below this line:
